    "More specifically, Yang-Cai and Rui (2021) used LDA to extract learners' topic concerns from 7836 MOOC (massive open online courses) review dataset.",
    "In educational context, our review findings indicate that most studies used LDA (Harden et al. 2019; Hong et al.",
    "2020; Hynninen et al. 2019; Ko et al.",
    "2021; Lim et al. 2017; Rääf et al.",
    "2021) to extract topics from qualitative dataset."
